1.0.3.name: wordpress/plumba
1.0.3.description:
Online poll plugin for WordPress. Add to any page or post! Add a new set of question with answers "Plumba" and save. Then choose the saved Plumba in your HTML-editor in WordPress. Your visitors can now make a vote at your page or post and the results are shown in realtime.

You can see the plugin in action here: Demo
